{"tid":1269494,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（法律討論）如果聽日比人打，可唔可以「自衛」？","createTime":"2019-06-30T14:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T15:00:31.000Z","uid":7542,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"93a66deda3d6072695f0264286d2f76e2fd5b7cd","tid":1269494,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:50:57.000Z","msg":"今日見到有唔少襲擊場面，唔知聽日大家會唔會遇到比人打嘅情況。<br />\n<br />\n<em><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">是日部份襲擊場面：</span></ins></em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2325587784358992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2325587784358992&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXCK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=8acefe84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2325587784358992</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190630/59774158?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=messenger&amp;utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F59774158%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dmessenger%26utm_source%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXCK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=e16b970c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F59774158%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dmessenger%26utm_source%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=17c24adf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190630/59774158?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=messenger&amp;utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_content=share_link</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/UnitedSocialPress/videos/vb.579827748716829/314190782791701/?type=2&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUnitedSocialPress%2Fvideos%2Fvb.579827748716829%2F314190782791701%2F%3Ftype%3D2%26theater&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXCK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=d1ac7b42\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/UnitedSocialPress/videos/vb.579827748716829/314190782791701/?type=2&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有好多人都問咩係「自衛」，如果比人打，到底可唔可以還手。<br />\n小弟試吓搵搵整合資料，希望幫到大家 （亦請高手 proof-read / cross-check）：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins>自衛</ins></em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em><ins>法律定義</ins></em></span><br />\n<br />\n「守衛或保護<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">自己</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">第三者</span></strong>或財物，免受他人引致的即將出現的傷害或傷害威脅而作出的行爲」(&quot;acting to guard or protect oneself, a third party, or property against imminent harm, or a threat of harm, by another&quot;) [1]。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em><ins>用途</ins></em></span><br />\n<br />\n如你用武力傷害他人 (例如襲擊你嘅人)，自衛可以係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>完全嘅抗辯 (&quot;complete defence&quot;)</strong></span>。意思即係如果你因為出手打施襲者而比人告普通襲擊，你可以話自己係自衛，如果法庭接納你就會完全甩罪。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em><ins>自衛條件</ins></em></span><br />\n<br />\n- 你出手係為咗防衛自己及阻止進一步傷害 [2]<br />\n- 你出手唔係為咗反擊或傷害個施襲者<br />\n- <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">合理武力</span></strong> [3]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em><ins>合理武力</ins></em></span><br />\n<br />\n法庭會考慮：<br />\n- 你嗰時係咪真係可以咁淡定咁，判斷應該用咩武力反擊先至合適 [4]<br />\n- 有無其他方法唔洗出拳都走得甩 [5] <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em><ins>處境</ins></em></span><br />\n<br />\n- 如果佢哋已經無再追打你，但你繼續打返佢哋，就唔可以話係自衛 [6]<br />\n- 就算對家嗰拳未打到嚟，只要你覺得佢真係準備出拳打落嚟，你都可以先作自衛，唔洗先捱佢一拳 [7]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">[1] Beckford v R [1988] AC 130<br />\n[2] R v Clegg [1995] 1 AC 482<br />\n[3] Palmer v R [1971] AC 814<br />\n[4] 或者法律嘅用字係：考慮迅速評估使用武力的正確程度的難度<br />\n[5] 或者法律嘅用字係：是否有任何合理逃出最初危險處境的合理方法<br />\n[6] Priestnall v Cornish [1979] Crim LR 310<br />\n[7] R v Deana (1909) 73 JP 255</span><br />\n<br />\n以上純為法律討論，各位法律界朋友請幫忙補充。"},{"pid":"1c3eeb055d1f0b9bfd807058098b09bc8e463f09","tid":1269494,"uid":97267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:51:51.000Z","msg":"合理定義唔係你定<br />\n<br />\n已經比佢講哂"},{"pid":"b118f07f8036e8ca82a9c66248beef0d127143c6","tid":1269494,"uid":258484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:53:17.000Z","msg":"其實好少會完全接納你 唔好諗多左"},{"pid":"bd00db804107c472238763b71d4604980ea30359","tid":1269494,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"「有無其他方法唔洗出拳都走得甩 [5] 」<br />\n可唔可以理解為被襲者有責任逃走？<br />\n咁如果對方係「襲擊致造成身體傷害」<br />\n可唔可以用武力制服佢交比警察？"},{"pid":"e6fab0111a66297df0b97bf2950cfa1829df2c6d","tid":1269494,"uid":222038,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:00:31.000Z","msg":"算把啦！你俾人打到頭破血流都好！差人見到咪叫打人既快走，然後登記你身份証，要你講唔追究先俾你走，否則一大堆罪名告你"}]}